          <cite class='member author entry-title'><a href="/people/mr-damian-green" title="Mr Damian Green">Mr. Damian Green</a></cite>
          <p class="first-para" id="S6CV0412P0-05124">To ask the Secretary of State for Education and Skills how many children have played truant in each month of the academic year 2002&#x2013;03 in each local education authority. [133694]</p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S6CV0412P0-05125'>
