          <p class="first-para" id="S6CV0412P0-05125">I refer the hon. Member to the reply I gave on <a href="/written_answers/2003/apr/30/pupil-absences#column_413w">30 April 2003,<span class="italic">Official Report</span>, column 413W</a>.</p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      
